Thank you for your commitment to Stone Arch Capital III, L.P. We are calling $26,011,790.68 to
make a platform investment in a leading marketer of highline, collectible automobiles and to pay
management fees and miscellaneous fund expenses. A detailed description of the new platform
investment will be included in the quarterly report following close of the transaction.

are giving you notice of a capital call for Stone Arch Capital III, L.P., a Delaware limited
